
As the original devicde is obsolete, it is usually emulated by the system chipset (by HPET or frankenstein IRQ routing).

RTC is accessed through CMOS variables.

→ hardware/interrupt[interrupts] usually routed to → hardware/PC/interrupts#irq[IRQ 8].

sa:

  → hardware/PC/real-time-clock,
  → hardware/APCI
